videos.headline: Melrose: Sharks can be labeled as winners now
videos.description: Barry Melrose says the Sharks making the Stanley Cup finals puts a stamp on the careers of Joe Thornton and Patrick Marleau and describes how emotional it can get in the traditional handshake line after a series.
